vulnerability.name: USN-7745-1
vulnerability.description: It was discovered that CUPS incorrectly handled authentication types other than Basic. An attacker could possibly use this issue to bypass authentication. (CVE-2025-58060)  It was discovered that CUPS incorrectly handled deserialization and validation of printer attributes. An attacker could possibly use this issue to cause a denial of service. (CVE-2025-58364)

statements.status_notes: Several security issues were fixed in CUPS.
